data.description: Stunning, modern farmhouse on 25 Ag exempt Acres with small pond. Open layout with decorative lighting, vaulted ceilings, wood beams, & every detail thoughtfully placed. 4 BR 3 Bath custom home. 2 primary en suites. Gorgeous kitchen has granite, an island, farm sink, coffee bar, walk-in pantry, & a scullery for all your storage & staging needs. Downstairs primary BR has tray ceilings, entry to patio, dual vanities, walk-in shower, & garden tub. You will love the washer & dryer in the huge closet! Mud room from garage. Split BR plan with walk-in closets downstairs. Roll-in Accessible shower. Upstairs space has full bathroom, perfect for 2nd primary BR, office, game room, man cave, theater, etc. Outdoor kitchen. Wooded creek. Pasture. RV parking. No mobile homes allowed, does have a 2nd water meter up near road to build another home. Completly fenced & cross fenced. Bring your animals, garden, build a pool or barn- so many options on your own TX ranch! 90 mi to DFW!
